Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.40,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:05.74,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:10.75,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:17.67,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:22.18,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.85,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:32.06,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.06,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:37.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:43.24,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.95,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:52.17,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.00,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.79,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:02.13,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:09.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.56,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.19,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.90,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.36,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
